This figure-skimming gown is the ultimate scene-stealer you’ve been dreaming about. Cut from a lightweight tulle and lined in soft satin, this dress is artfully embellished with light-reflecting mirrored mosaic pieces and features a deep illusion v-neckline suspended from delicate spaghetti straps. From the daring side slit to the sexy corset-style lacing and pooling train, you are sure to look perfect from every angle.

The body skimming silhouette features a plunging v-neckline with illusion mesh and embellished double crossover straps that turn to reveal a low, open v-shaped back. The skirt descends to an elegant pooling floor-length hem.
